  <summary date="2018-04-24T04:00:00Z" status="Introduced in House">Healthy Environment for Children Act

This bill prohibits the Environmental Protection Agency from reducing, consolidating, or terminating the offices and activities (e.g., intramural grants, extramural grants, and research) of the National Center for Environmental Research.</summary>
